Steps:
1. Navigate to GraphQL playground: ${BACK_URL}/graphql
2. Execute whiteLabelingSettings query with footerLinks field:
query {
  whiteLabelingSettings(
    organizationId: "<org-id>"
    storeId: "B2B-store"
  ) {
    footerLinks {
      title
      url
      priority
      childItems {
        title
        url
        priority
      }
    }
  }
}
3. Verify response structure
4. Verify data matches admin configuration

