1. Navigate to GraphQL playground
2. Execute pageContext query:
query {
  pageContext(
    storeId: "B2B-store"
    organizationId: "<org-id>"
    cultureName: "en-US"
  ) {
    slugInfo { ... }
    store { ... }
    whiteLabelingSettings {
      logoUrl
      faviconUrl
      themePresetName
      footerLinks { title url childItems { title url } }
      mainMenuLinks { title url priority childItems { title url priority } }
    }
    user { ... }
  }
}
3. Verify whiteLabelingSettings embedded in pageContext
4. Verify mainMenuLinks field present
